list.abstract: Rice，米，樱井有纪、村田一弘的二人团。2001年成立的他们奋斗了人生的大部分时光，二人都是14岁开始组Band，一开始的挫折并没有打垮他们，一直努力到了现在的Rice。
rice，英语词汇，基本释义为稻、稻谷。

yingyinNormal.en: 1,533 miles away in southeast Yunnan, the locals have their own agricultural mountain to overcome: how to grow China's greatest staple rice?
yingyinNormal.zh: 两千五百公里外，西南部的云南省，对于农业，当地人也有其独特的艰难险阻，即如何种植中国最重要的主食——大米。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, my God, this is the best sushi I've ever had. For the first time, I can taste the yellowtail from the sea and then the rice from the land, then back to the sea for the seaweed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的天，这是我吃过最好吃的寿司。我第一次能吃出海产的黄狮鱼味和陆产的大米味，然后又回到海产的海苔味。

yingyinNormal.en: Now to go with the sea bass, I've got some wild rice and basmati rice.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我用来给海鲈鱼配餐的，是菰米饭和印度香米饭。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, I've got here some jasmine rice. Yep. I'm using a variety of rice called Jasmine, because I like the nutty flavor, but any long-grain cooked rice will do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我这里有一些泰国香米。是的。我用的米叫做泰国香米，我喜欢它的坚果香味，但只要是长粒米饭都能用。

yingyinNormal.en: If you haven't got this, then you can use balsamic vinegar. Like us do as well. Or even rice vinegar. Cos you like rice vinegar.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果买不到，也可用香油醋代替，米醋也行，因为英国人喜欢用米醋。

yingyinNormal.en: Then to make a simple dressing, the soy, the black rice vinegar, which is made from glutinous rice, but you can use balsamic vinegar.
yingyinNormal.zh: 最后加一点调料，这种酱料，这种黑米醋，用糯米制成，不过你也可以用香醋。

yingyinNormal.en: That's the best egg fried rice I've ever tasted, I have to say.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我得说这是我吃过的最好吃的蛋炒饭。

yingyinNormal.en: Next ingredient for the egg fried rice is some chopped spring onion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 蛋炒饭的下一个配料是剁碎的大葱。

yingyinNormal.en: Take your pets and your porcelain, Sidao, and return to the rice paddies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 带上你的宝贝宠物和瓷器，似道，回家种田去吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh my God. Oh I know, my God, this is so, this rice is so... I am so good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天哪，我知道，天哪，这个饭好… 我的手艺真好。

yingyinNormal.en: So about a tablespoon of Shaoxing rice wine. You can always use dry sherry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大约一汤匙绍兴米酒，你也可以用干雪利酒。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm going to serve up a little bit of the rice. Some of this delicious sauce.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要盛一点炒饭出来，加上点儿美味的酱汁。

yingyinNormal.en: Put some chopped garlic into a bowl. Some Shaoxing rice wine or dry sherry. A drizzle of light soy sauce for some saltiness. And then a little bit of Chinkiang black rice vinegar.
yingyinNormal.zh: 切一点大蒜放进碗里，加少许绍兴米酒或干雪利酒，倒入一些生抽用于增加咸味，再倒入少许镇江香醋。

yingyinNormal.en: I wish I could believe you. I also wish there wasn't a mouse living in Rice Sheldon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也希望能相信你的话，我还希望米袋谢尔顿的身体里没有住着一只老鼠。

yingyinNormal.en: To grow their crops, they hand carved rice paddies into the mountains to trap the water.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为了种植庄稼，她们用双手在一座座山上造出梯田，以此蓄水肥田。

yingyinNormal.en: I've got some rice and I've got some vegetables. Pre-cooked some broccoli and some asparagus.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我准备了米饭和蔬菜，这是提前煮熟的西兰花和芦笋。

yingyinNormal.en: If you can't get Shao Hsing rice wine, then I would use dry sherry. That's a great alternative.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果没有绍兴米酒，你可以使用干雪利酒，也是个不错的替代品。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, not exactly alone. I do have a 50 pound sack of rice with one of Sheldon's T-shirts on it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也不算独居，有一个穿着谢尔顿T恤的50磅米袋子陪着我。

yingyinNormal.en: Add a drop more rice wine or dry sherry, some light soy sauce, and freshen it up with lime zest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再加入一滴米酒或干雪利酒，一些生抽和青柠末，给菜提味。

yingyinNormal.en: Make a batch of Nian Gao, steamed cakes made with rice flour, which are said to bring good luck.
yingyinNormal.zh: 做一些由米粉蒸出来的年糕，据说这样会带来好运。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Ferraro suggests the results may transfer to other parts of Asia, due to commonalities such as the importance of growing <highlight>rice</highlight> and market access.
examination_example.sentence_trans: Ferraro 认为，由于种植水稻的重要性和市场准入等共同点，这些结果可能会转移到亚洲其他地区。

examination_example.sentence: Typically, if rains are delayed, people may clear land to plant more <highlight>rice</highlight> to supplement their harvests.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 通常情况下，如果降雨延迟，人们可能会清理土地，种植更多的水稻来补充收成。

examination_example.sentence: Production of corn, cotton, <highlight>rice</highlight>, soybeans, and wheat has been largely mechanized, but many high-value, labor-intensive crops, such as strawberries, need labor.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 玉米、棉花、水稻、大豆和小麦的生产已基本实现机械化，但许多高价值、劳动密集型的作物，如草莓，需要劳动力。

word_usage.usage: rice为不可数名词，“一粒米”用a grain of rice表达，“多粒米”用grains of rice。
